      • Car

        public Car(int id,
           java.lang.String make,
           java.lang.String model,
           int year,
           java.lang.String color,
           int ownerId,
           int price,
           java.lang.String description,
           java.lang.String carType,
           java.util.List<Image> images)
        This is the constructor for the Car object. It requires all of the car information to create.
        Parameters:
        id - The id of the car.
        make - The make of the car.
        model - The model of the car.
        year - The year of the car.
        color - The color of the car.
        ownerId - The id of the owner of the car.
        price - The price per day of the car.
        description - The description of the car.
        carType - The body type of the car.
        images - A list of Image objects of the car.
